      "source": [
        "## Fungsi\n",
        "\n",
        "Buatlah fungsi `jumlahkan` yang menerima input `n` lalu menghitung\n",
        "\n",
        "$$1 + 2 + 3 + \\dots + n = \\text{ ?}$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "843b7ac8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def jumlahkan(n):\n",
        "  hasil = 0\n",
        "  for i in range(1, n+1):\n",
        "    hasil = hasil + i\n",
        "  return hasil"
      ],
      "id": "2d80c2ca",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "executionInfo": {
          "elapsed": 354,
          "status": "ok",
          "timestamp": 1731053302588,
          "user": {
            "displayName": "Komputasi Kelas B",
            "userId": "06926514210856024628"
          },
          "user_tz": -420
        }
      },
      "source": [
        "print(jumlahkan(3))"
      ],
      "id": "beb5b294",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "executionInfo": {
          "elapsed": 339,
          "status": "ok",
          "timestamp": 1731053373399,
          "user": {
            "displayName": "Komputasi Kelas B",
            "userId": "06926514210856024628"
          },
          "user_tz": -420
        }
      },
      "source": [
        "print(jumlahkan(100))"
      ],
      "id": "15621f14",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Fungsi Rekursif\n",
        "\n",
        "Barisan Fibonacci: 0, 1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, ...\n",
        "\n",
        "$$F_0 = 0, \\quad F_1 = 1$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$F_n = F_{n-1} + F_{n-2}$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "c60cedec"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def fib(n):\n",
        "  if (n == 0):\n",
        "    return 0\n",
        "  elif (n == 1):\n",
        "    return 1\n",
        "  else:\n",
        "    return fib(n-1) + fib(n-2)"
      ],
